dc_description_s: This data layer represents zoning for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2020 and includes the layers 'Portage_Airports_2020', 'Portage_Shoreland_2020' and 'Portage_Zoning_General_2020'. Shoreland: [Polygon data depicting shoreland zone for lakes and impoundments. Water bodies are included if they have a history of holding water in 2000, 2005, 2010 Portage County Aerial photography.]General: [The zoning classification defined at the parcel level, but typically managed in larger units.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
